   "source": "<ROUTINE JAPANESE-PHRASE? (\"AUX\" (CNT 0) (LEN <GET ,JAPANESE-PHRASES 0>)\n\t\t\t   (TBL <REST ,JAPANESE-PHRASES 2>))\n\t <REPEAT ()\n\t\t <COND (<EQUAL? .CNT .LEN> <RFALSE>)\n\t\t       (<MATCH-INTQUOTE? <GET .TBL 0>>\n\t\t\t<RETURN <GET .TBL 1>>)\n\t\t       (ELSE\n\t\t\t<SET CNT <+ .CNT 2>>\n\t\t\t<SET TBL <REST .TBL 4>>)>>>"
