   "source": "<ROUTINE DESCRIBE-START (OBJ N)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .OBJ ,HERE>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,D-BIT ,PERSON>\n\t\t       <TELL \"You see \">)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <TELL \"There \">\n\t\t       <COND (.N <TELL \"are \">)\n\t\t\t     (ELSE <TELL \"is \">)>)>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .OBJ ,PLAYER>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,D-BIT ,WEARBIT>\n\t\t       <TELL \"\u000bYou are wearing \">)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <TELL \"You are carrying \">)>)\n\t       (<FSET? .OBJ ,PERSON>\n\t\t;<COND (<NOT <FSET? .OBJ ,NOTHEBIT>>\n\t\t       <TELL \"The \">)> ;\"hand is only one this clause catches\"\n\t\t<TELL CTHE .OBJ \" has \">)\n\t       (<FSET? .OBJ ,SURFACEBIT>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? .OBJ ,LADDER> <TELL \"Stand\">)\n\t\t      (ELSE <TELL \"Sitt\">)>\n\t\t<TELL \"ing on \" THE .OBJ>\n\t\t<COND (.N <TELL \" are \">)\n\t\t      (ELSE <TELL \" is \">)>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<TELL CTHE .OBJ \" contains \">)>>"
