   "source": "<ROUTINE SEA-CHAIR-F (RARG)\n\t <COND (<RARG? BEG>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? WALK>\n\t\t       <YOULL-HAVE-TO \"get out of the sea chair\">)\n\t\t      (<VERB? STAND>\n\t\t       <B-STAND>\n\t\t       <MOVE ,WINNER ,HERE>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"You rise to your feet.\" CR>)>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? BOARD SIT>\n\t\t       <COND (<NOT <IN? ,WINNER ,SEA-CHAIR>>\n\t\t\t      <MOVE ,WINNER ,SEA-CHAIR>\n\t\t\t      <B-SIT>\n\t\t\t      <TELL\n\"You are now sitting in the sea chair.\" CR>)>)>)>>"
