   "source": "<ROUTINE MAZE-MOUSE-F (TRM \"AUX\" (DIR <>) WX WY\n\t\t       (BX <GET ,MAZE-BOX-TBL 1>) (BY <GET ,MAZE-BOX-TBL 0>))\n\t <SET WY\n\t      <+ <WINGET ,MAZE-WINDOW ,WTOP>\n\t\t ,YOFFSET\n\t\t <* ,Y .BY>\n\t\t </ .BY 2>>>\n\t <SET WX\n\t      <+ <WINGET ,MAZE-WINDOW ,WLEFT>\n\t\t ,XOFFSET\n\t\t <* ,X .BX>\n\t\t </ .BX 2>>>\n\t <SET WY <- ,MOUSE-LOC-Y .WY>>\n\t <SET WX <- ,MOUSE-LOC-X .WX>>\n\t <COND (<G=? .WX 0> ;\"right side\"\n\t\t<COND (<L? .WY 0> ;\"top right\"\n\t\t       <SET WY <- .WY>>\n\t\t       <COND (<G? .WX <* .WY 3>>\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,EAST-STR>)\n\t\t\t     (<G? .WY <* .WX 3>>\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,NORTH-STR>)\n\t\t\t     (ELSE\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,NE-STR>)>)\n\t\t      (ELSE ;\"bottom right\"\n\t\t       <COND (<G? .WX <* .WY 3>>\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,EAST-STR>)\n\t\t\t     (<G? .WY <* .WX 3>>\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,SOUTH-STR>)\n\t\t\t     (ELSE\n\t\t\t      <SET DIR ,SE-STR>)>)>)\n\t       (<L? .WY 0> ;\"top left\"\n\t\t<SET WY <- .WY>>\n\t\t<SET WX <- .WX>>\n\t\t<COND (<G? .WX <* .WY 3>>\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,WEST-STR>)\n\t\t      (<G? .WY <* .WX 3>>\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,NORTH-STR>)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,NW-STR>)>)\n\t       (ELSE ;\"bottom left\"\n\t\t<SET WX <- .WX>>\n\t\t<COND (<G? .WX <* .WY 3>>\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,WEST-STR>)\n\t\t      (<G? .WY <* .WX 3>>\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,SOUTH-STR>)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <SET DIR ,SW-STR>)>)>\n\t <COND (<AND <L=? .WX </ .BX 2>> <L=? .WY </ .BY 2>>>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (.DIR\n\t\t<ADD-TO-INPUT .DIR 13>\n\t\t<RETURN 13>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
