   "source": "<ROUTINE MPUTC (X Y \"OPT\" (VAL <>) \"AUX\" OVAL)\n\t <COND (<VALID .X .Y>\n\t\t<SET OVAL <MGETB .X .Y>>\n\t\t<COND (<NOT .VAL>\n\t\t       <SET VAL .OVAL>\n\t\t       <COND (<MSTREET? .VAL>\n\t\t\t      <COND (<AND <EQUAL? .X ,XSTART>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <EQUAL? .Y ,YSTART>>\n\t\t\t\t     <SET VAL ,P-MAZE-CASTLE ;!\\C>)\n\t\t\t\t    (<AND <EQUAL? .X ,XGOAL>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <EQUAL? .Y ,YGOAL>>\n\t\t\t\t     <SET VAL ,P-MAZE-DOCK ;!\\D>)\n\t\t\t\t    (<AND <EQUAL? .X ,XFISH>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <EQUAL? .Y ,YFISH>>\n\t\t\t\t     <SET VAL ,P-MAZE-FISH ;!\\F>)\n\t\t\t\t    (ELSE <SET VAL ,P-MAZE-STREET ;!\\ >)>)\n\t\t\t     (ELSE\n\t\t\t      <SET VAL ,P-MAZE-WALL ;!\\*>)>)>\n\t\t<SET VAL <BOR .VAL <BAND .OVAL ,MWALL>>>\n\t\t<COND (<NOT <EQUAL? .VAL .OVAL>>\n\t\t       <MPUTB .X .Y .VAL>\n\t\t       <DISPLAY-MAZE-PIC <BAND .VAL 127> .Y .X>)>)>>"
