   "source": "<ROUTINE GENERIC-GRAY-F (R F)\n\t <COND (<FSET? ,SECOND-GRAY ,DEAD> ,RANDOM-GRAYS)\n\t       (<FSET? ,GRAY-LEADER ,DEAD> ,SECOND-GRAY)\n\t       (ELSE <RFALSE>)>>"
