   "source": "<ROUTINE PUT-DOWN-TOWEL ()\n\t <COND (<IN? ,TOWEL ,WINNER>\n\t\t<MOVE ,TOWEL ,HERE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"First, you put down the towel so it won't get wet.  \">)>>"
