   "file": "verbs.zil",
   "line": 3830,
   "endLine": 3844,
   "source": "<ROUTINE V-STAND (\"AUX\" AV)\n\t <COND (<PRSO? <> ,ROOMS>\n\t\t<SET AV <LOC ,WINNER>>\n\t\t<COND (<AND <FSET? .AV ,VEHBIT>\n\t\t\t    <NOT <EQUAL? .AV ,QUILT>>>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"You shouldn't stand up inside \" A .AV \".\" CR>)\n\t\t      (<B-NOT-STANDING?>\n\t\t       <B-STAND>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"You stand up.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <TELL ,YOU-ARE \" standing.\" CR>)>)\n\t       (ELSE \n\t\t<HACK-HACK \"Holding up\">)>>"
