   "source": "<ROUTINE V-SIT ()\n\t <COND (<NOT <PRSO? <> ,ROOMS>>\n\t\t<TELL ,WASTE-OF-TIME>)\n\t       (<B-NOT-STANDING?>\n\t\t<COND (<B-SITTING?>\n\t\t       <TELL G\"You already are.\" CR>)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <B-SIT>\n\t\t       <TELL \"You sit up.\" CR>)>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<B-SIT>\n\t\t<TELL \"You sit down.\" CR>)>>"
