   "endLine": 4067,
   "source": "<ROUTINE COLOR-OFFSET (TMP)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .TMP ,C-WHITE> <SET TMP 1>)\n\t       (<G? .TMP ,C-WHITE> <SET TMP <- .TMP 1>>)>\n\t .TMP>"
