   "source": "<ROUTINE COLOR-MENU-F (TMP M)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .TMP 1> ;\"white is really 9, not 1\"\n\t\t<SET TMP ,C-WHITE>)\n\t       (<G? .TMP 8>\n\t\t<SET TMP <+ .TMP 1>>)>\n\t .TMP>"
