   "source": "<ROUTINE ROCKY-SHORE-F (RARG)\n\t <COND (<RARG? ENTER>\n\t\t<SEARCH-PARTY-FOLLOWS>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<RARG? BEG>\n\t\t<COND (<AND <P? WALK P?SOUTH>\n\t\t\t    <FSET? ,CLIFF-PATH ,TOUCHBIT>>\n\t\t       <YABU-PREVENTS>)>)>>"
