  "YAMAZAKI-ATTACKS": {
   "name": "YAMAZAKI-ATTACKS",
   "kind": "global",
   "file": "mariko.zil",
   "line": 449,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"The Captain leaps forward, his sword a whirling arc directed at your\nhead!\" \"The Captain swings his sword, chopping viciously at your knees.\" \"The Captain charges at you, his sword pointed straight at your belly.\" \"The Captain screams \"Yaemon!\" and begins an overhand blow toward\nyour head.\">"
  },
  "SWORD-ATTACKS": {
   "name": "SWORD-ATTACKS",
   "kind": "constant",
   "file": "mariko.zil",
   "line": 543,
   "value": "<LTABLE 0 \"You swing, wishing for luck, for good karma, for a pistol, by\nGod!  He parries, but the force of your blow is strong, and the tip\nmanages to carve into his wrist.\" \"You hold the blade before you, stabbing almost wildly with it, wondering\nwhy his attack is so formal.  You see an opening and plunge madly\nforward, wounding him in the chest.\" \"You interpose your blade, and there is a ringing, almost bell-like\ncrash as they meet.  You slide your blade around and manage to wound\nhim.  He seems almost surprised.\" \"Leaping and yelling, you charge him, and in an astonishing flurry he\nfights back, executing a daring turn and riposte, but he's off balance\nand you slice the back of his calf.\">"
  },
